{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01KhD2WiKYejchWVrddxV4sh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me read the key documentation files that are most likely to need updating based on these changes:\n\n1. `docs/USAGE.md` - likely documents CLI commands\n2. `CLAUDE.md` - project overview (already read in context)\n3. Maybe `docs/workflows.md` if it mentions task pipeline\n\nThe key changes are:\n1. New `cloche tasks` CLI command\n2. New web API endpoint `GET /api/projects/{name}/tasks`\n3. Run ID format changed from `<workflow>-<adj>-<noun>` to `<workflow>-<adj>-<noun>-<hex>`\n\n\n4. Several new types and methods added to the core loop and handler logic to support task snapshots and state tracking.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":9950,"cache_read_input_tokens":14530,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":9950},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9eafd946-92ce-4081-bfc6-e705f31b605b","uuid":"04547e4e-8d90-4994-97cc-7540e76cba19"}
